            "title": "港股開升37點  京東系飆  嗶哩嗶哩跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股恒生指數開升37點或0.15%，報25358點，恒生科技指數開升22點或0.47%，報4818點，恒生國企指數開報8469點，升18點或0.21%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">大市成交43.37億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：京東外賣官微\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/02/20260302_FI_source-web_09618-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：京東外賣官微\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/02/20260302_FI_source-web_09618-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：京東外賣官微</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">京東(09618)升1.6%，報98.5元; 京東健康(06618)升3.58%，報49.2元 ; 京東物流(02618)飆6.43%，報10.93元。京東系昨公布業績。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">嗶嗶嗶哩(096267)低開2.75%，報204.8元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">攜程(09961)升3.18%，報402.4元，成交入20大。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">友邦保險(01299)升1.06%，報86元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">非凡領越(00933)預告虧轉盈，升1.64%，報0.62元。汽車之家(02518)揚3.46%，報36.5元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">紫金(02899)跌1.32%，報40.32元。</p>\n</div>",
